  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Valuing Respect, How to evaluate business repect for HR</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UN Guiding Principles on Business and Human Rights (UNGPs) set out the responsibility of all companies to respect human rights across their operations and value chains. While people in any country can be affected by negative impacts from business activities, the large majority of those most severely impacted live in developing countries. Concerted and large-scale progress in reducing these impacts is critical in order to achieve many of the Sustainable Development Goals</narrative>
  </description>
